{"tid":316380,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"動物傳心 v.s. 風水命理","createTime":"2017-07-10T16:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T18:02:02.000Z","uid":18936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33b0e2b17881984e28e8cea12443e55c6b02265e","tid":316380,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"兩樣都唔科學 但點解後者多人信 <br />\n而且又幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和平討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7797186282477b1743f191a97b9f5470ff73498","tid":316380,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩樣都唔科學 但點解後者多人信 <br />\n而且又幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和平討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5aceef669bbd07700d4da615a9beafafb62258e1","tid":316380,"uid":29702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53d2c68e3ce8bdbbed14a4ef102eadf6537759fc","tid":316380,"uid":29702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e807dd61511f0470a04af08371e5fcd483b08c5","tid":316380,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"015f39c3dcf493c7bde27ba2fc627df8ecfafb7b","tid":316380,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風水佬用自己套理論<br />\n好少借科學過橋<br />\n前者相反</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果「識」動物傳心嗰班友識得用一種近似風水命理既理由做support <br />\n其實都可以上到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b0b034c4537bfdf717e2adc8777715c1fc5995","tid":316380,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec86b43ae9457b7dfdd3ed17c27cddffccdc4d8e","tid":316380,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"因為後者存在得耐<br />\n如果動物傳心唔收皮<br />\n過多幾十年 <br />\n都會有好多信徒"},{"pid":"d3886b496c7b8a288350dfc08958eb8c277a0a42","tid":316380,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"咁中醫點解多人信？<br />\n<br />\n同樣原因啫，一切迷信都不離自圓其說、建立優越性、從眾效應。<br />\n<br />\n嚟嚟去去都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n動物傳心衰在出世太慢，今日資訊流通太快，好難昆到一大班人再成為主流。"},{"pid":"84c62636b08607eb47476b86e04d3ffc6e4beef2","tid":316380,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"風水佬會話你知，信則有，不信則無<br />\n傳心同你講佢係科學，係真既，你信啦"},{"pid":"20b0f169b0fdd3dd00b220298dcbc589af4f66cf","tid":316380,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"屌你動物傳心邊個驗證到堅定流?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />梗係吹得就吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fcfd0821fb24ec982e535c04f6cc6009b01230","tid":316380,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:08:50.000Z","msg":"風水仲可以叫做千年統計出嚟嘅結果，嗰d咩撚野動物傳心師真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee565769482643ed54808ecbaacae84c59203998","tid":316380,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:10:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a412c2a86